{"tid":942804,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣36F辣媽與12歲兒共浴　掀倫理爭議","createTime":"2018-12-16T05:20:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-16T07:44:28.000Z","uid":141060,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"836b2811a7d271addd099c284d441934a084ea15","tid":942804,"uid":141060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T05:20:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20181216/photo/bkn-20181216122254858-1216_00952_001_01p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20181216%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181216122254858-1216_00952_001_01p.jpg&h=72b78deb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20181216/photo/bkn-20181216122254858-1216_00952_001_02p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20181216%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181216122254858-1216_00952_001_02p.jpg&h=4b3ab12e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n台灣擁有36F驕人上圍的朱姓單親辣媽「紫米」，近日於網上分享一張與其12歲兒子「全裸共浴」的照片，拍照期間二人又做出「V字」手勢，可見母子感情融洽。紫米更指，每周會和兒子「共浴」一次，事件引起網民熱議。<br />\n<br />\n紫米發相原意其實是想與網民聊聊育兒經，了解其他家長有否與孩子共浴的習慣，「你們都跟孩子們一起洗澡嗎？洗到幾歲呢？」紫米表示，雖然兒子已經12歲，但母子倆一周至少共浴一次。她認為自覺需要多點陪兒子，亦很珍惜和他一起洗澡的日子，「當他會主動拒絕你時，就是進入青春期了」。<br />\n<br />\n她亦稱，日本人也會一家人共浴，希望網民不要戴有色眼鏡去看，更稱當兒子習慣看媽媽的胴體，就不會對女性身體產生好奇，對其心理會較更健康。不過她亦坦承，若然換成父女，就似乎不太適合。<br />\n<br />\n對於辣媽母子共浴一事，有大批網民批評，指孩子快到青春期，如此年紀下還和母親赤裸共浴有違倫理，並質疑「這樣不會出問題嗎？」、「現在孩子發育得早，這樣感覺怪怪的！」<br />\n<br />\n不過有網民就支持稱，母子共浴可增進親子關係，同時可灌輸正確的性觀念，事件至今仍引起廣泛迴響。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cbda7a67554f3cdb2538f953b7e7f180c4eb565","tid":942804,"uid":141151,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T05:21:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">不過她亦坦承，若然換成父女，就似乎不太適合。</span><br />\n<br />\n點解父女就唔適合<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n歧視阿爸定阿女？"},{"pid":"bbb5c5f7759635c2a6d52afa359ee139d85f9406","tid":942804,"uid":149496,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T05:22:45.000Z","msg":"連登&gt;&gt;公海&gt;&gt;連登<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://4.bp.blogspot.com/-tyFzN0kTdQ8/U5FFxjvhJEI/AAAAAAAAhWk/8Xi0V-Vo_EU/s1600/4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F4.bp.blogspot.com%2F-tyFzN0kTdQ8%2FU5FFxjvhJEI%2FAAAAAAAAhWk%2F8Xi0V-Vo_EU%2Fs1600%2F4.jpg&h=e598f65f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"60235b7cf35b1e634e308ab117d409fca01b8c90","tid":942804,"uid":141060,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T05:23:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/jAYDf_iXzUL9rtNuhkHBNQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-TW/homerun/news_tvbs_com_tw_938/47cfddba14d12902a30dcacfd0c35029\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FjAYDf_iXzUL9rtNuhkHBNQ--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-TW%2Fhomerun%2Fnews_tvbs_com_tw_938%2F47cfddba14d12902a30dcacfd0c35029&h=b5658aad&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"222961ad2174e5cfae32bc7e80952b9165bb993f","tid":942804,"uid":25345,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T05:23:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/11/23/IJzNho.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F11%2F23%2FIJzNho.jpg&h=e534a4f4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ddc0bf553735c24374cf65002102c25a5429972d","tid":942804,"uid":121580,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"quote":{"pid":"4cbda7a67554f3cdb2538f953b7e7f180c4eb565","tid":942804,"uid":141151,"like":20,"dislike"